('EMAIL_SEQUENCE: La sequence d onboarding ideale: J0 bienvenue, J1 quick win, J3 cas client, J5 feature avancee, J7 CTA upgrade.', 'Onboarding email: J0 welcome, J1 win, J3 cas, J5 feature, J7 CTA', 'email', 'best_practice', 0.88, 'massive_boost_23', 'system'),
('EMAIL_SEQUENCE: La sequence de nurturing B2B: 1/semaine pendant 8 semaines. Alterner contenu educatif et cas clients.', 'Nurturing B2B: 1/sem × 8 sem. Alterner edu + cas', 'email', 'best_practice', 0.85, 'massive_boost_23', 'system'),
('EMAIL_SEQUENCE: La sequence de reactivation: J0 ce qui a change, J3 cas client recent, J7 offre speciale, J14 dernier rappel.', 'Reactivation: J0 news, J3 cas, J7 offre, J14 rappel', 'email', 'best_practice', 0.82, 'massive_boost_23', 'system'),
('EMAIL_SEQUENCE: La sequence post-achat: J0 merci, J3 guide utilisation, J7 demande avis, J14 cross-sell, J30 referral.', 'Post-achat: J0 merci, J3 guide, J7 avis, J14 cross-sell, J30 referral', 'email', 'best_practice', 0.88, 'massive_boost_23', 'system'),
('EMAIL_SEQUENCE: La sequence de pre-lancement: J-14 teaser, J-7 behind-the-scenes, J-3 countdown, J-1 derniere chance, J0 lancement.', 'Pre-lancement: J-14 teaser → J0 lancement', 'email', 'best_practice', 0.85, 'massive_boost_23', 'system'),
('CONTENT_FRAMEWORK: Le framework Hook-Story-Offer pour les posts: accrocher, raconter, proposer. Fonctionne sur toutes les plateformes.', 'Hook-Story-Offer = universel toutes plateformes', 'content', 'best_practice', 0.88, 'massive_boost_23', 'system'),
('CONTENT_FRAMEWORK: Le framework BAB (Before-After-Bridge): montrer le avant, le apres, et le pont (votre solution).', 'BAB: avant → apres → pont/solution', 'content', 'best_practice', 0.85, 'massive_boost_23', 'system'),
('CONTENT_FRAMEWORK: Le framework 4P (Promise, Picture, Proof, Push) pour les pages de vente longues.', '4P: Promise, Picture, Proof, Push pour sales pages', 'content', 'best_practice', 0.82, 'massive_boost_23', 'system'),
('CONTENT_FRAMEWORK: Le framework PASTOR (Problem, Amplify, Story, Testimony, Offer, Response) de Ray Edwards.', 'PASTOR: Problem → Amplify → Story → Testimony → Offer → Response', 'content', 'best_practice', 0.80, 'massive_boost_23', 'system'),
