('METRICS_PRODUCT: Le DAU/WAU/MAU ratio montre la frequence d utilisation. DAU/MAU > 30% = usage quotidien sain.', 'DAU/MAU > 30% = usage quotidien sain', 'ceo', 'insight', 0.85, 'massive_boost_23', 'system'),
